WEBVTT

00:04.560 --> 00:07.560
Xu'er, who do you want as your teacher?

00:08.080 --> 00:09.800
Do I need to ask personally?

00:11.520 --> 00:12.160
Your son

00:15.200 --> 00:17.560
Your son has always admired Grand General Zhu Yuanzhi

00:19.760 --> 00:21.320
The Second Prince

00:21.800 --> 00:23.360
Is more like Your Majesty

00:24.080 --> 00:26.760
Xu'er now has widespread support in the army

00:27.120 --> 00:29.160
Zhu Yuanzhi is the commander of the three armies

00:29.680 --> 00:31.840
He has always been close to the Second Prince

00:32.800 --> 00:35.080
If I were still here, this wouldn't be a problem

00:36.080 --> 00:38.720
But now, my time is running out

00:39.560 --> 00:41.120
If I depart

00:41.360 --> 00:44.280
Will Xu'er obey his elder brother's orders?
